{
    "id": null,
    "uid": "storage-memory",
    "title": "💾 Storage & Memory Usage",
    "description": "Database storage, memory usage, and resource consumption by component",
    "tags": [
        "storage",
        "memory",
        "database"
    ],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 38,
    "version": 3,
    "refresh": "30s",
    "time": {
        "from": "now-6h",
        "to": "now"
    },
    "panels": [
        {
            "id": 100,
            "title": "📚 Guía de Componentes de Almacenamiento",
            "type": "text",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 5,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 0
            },
            "options": {
                "mode": "markdown",
                "content": "## ¿Qué almacena cada componente?\n\n| Componente | Qué almacena | Escala con... | Tamaño típico |\n|------------|--------------|---------------|---------------|\n| **Qdrant** | Vectores de documentos (embeddings 384-dim) | Nº de chunks de documentos | ~1MB por cada 100 docs |\n| **PostgreSQL** | Conversaciones, usuarios, historial, estados | Nº de conversaciones | Crece lento (~1KB/conversación) |\n| **Redis** | Cache de respuestas LLM, tokens temporales | Requests repetidos | Auto-limpia (TTL 1h) |\n| **Backend** | 4 Workers Python (Modelos ML x4) | Fijo al iniciar | **40-50GB RAM** |\n| **Ollama** | Modelos LLM (llama3.1, llava) en GPU | Modelos descargados | 5-15GB VRAM |\n\n> **Nota**: El Backend Memory alto (45GB) es **NORMAL** con 4 workers (Production Mode)."
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "🧠 Backend Memory",
            "description": "Memoria RAM del proceso Python (4 Workers)",
            "type": "stat",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 4,
                "w": 6,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 5
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "process_resident_memory_bytes{job=\"rag-backend\"}",
                    "legendFormat": "RSS Memory",
                    "refId": "A"
                }
            ],
            "options": {
                "reduceOptions": {
                    "calcs": [
                        "last"
                    ],
                    "fields": "",
                    "values": false
                },
                "colorMode": "background",
                "graphMode": "area"
            },
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "bytes",
                    "thresholds": {
                        "mode": "absolute",
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "green",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "yellow",
                                "value": 40000000000
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "red",
                                "value": 80000000000
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                }
            }
        },
