        {
            "id": 7,
            "title": "💡 Cuándo preocuparse [RTX 5090 Edition]",
            "type": "text",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 7,
                "w": 6,
                "x": 18,
                "y": 9
            },
            "options": {
                "mode": "markdown",
                "content": "### ⚠️ Alertas:\n\n**Backend > 80GB**\n- Reiniciar backend\n\n**Memory creciendo**\n- Posible memory leak\n\n**GPU VRAM > 30GB**\n- Límite físico de RTX 5090\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Normal (Producción):\n- Backend: 40-50GB (4 Workers)\n- Indexer: 1-4GB\n- Qdrant: 100-500MB"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "title": "🔄 CPU Usage",
            "description": "Uso de CPU por proceso",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 6,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 16
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "(sum(rate(process_cpu_seconds_total{job=\"rag-backend\"}[5m])) / 64) * 100",
                    "legendFormat": "Backend CPU % (normalized)",
                    "refId": "A"
                },
                {
                    "expr": "(rate(process_cpu_seconds_total{job=\"rag-indexer\"}[5m]) / 64) * 100",
                    "legendFormat": "Indexer CPU % (normalized)",
                    "refId": "B"
                }
            ],
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "list",
                    "placement": "bottom"
                }
            },
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
                        "fillOpacity": 10
